title: 115: The Aldi Haul Episode: September '20 Edition
itunes:title: The Aldi Haul Episode: September '20 Edition
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa, Mikey, and Jamie are taste-testing finds like the BEST turkey pepperoni ever, a killer queso dip, a yummy salmon burger, chicken fajitas with a kick, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, an everything bagel with only 110 calories!!! So don’t wait any longer… Push play now! And when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the products mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: We went back to Aldi and boy did we find some GREAT products! It might be our best “HAULDI” ever…
